    "encrypted": "false",
    "display_name": "Agricultural Analyst",
    "long_instructions": "## Ana Souza, Agricultural Analyst 📊\r\n<br/>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>📍 Location:</strong> São Paulo, Brazil </p><br/>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>🏢 Workplace:</strong> AgroTech Solutions </p><br/>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\">💼<strong> Expertise:</strong> Data analysis, farm productivity, smart agriculture </p><br/>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>🔍 How I Use AI:</strong> \"I analyze the data collected by Solix Ag Robotics to help farmers make better decisions. The robot tracks crop health, soil conditions, and pest activity, allowing us to predict problems before they happen. AI-driven insights like these are transforming modern farming.\" </p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n\r\n## Do This:\r\n\r\n<ol style=\"font-size:16px\">\r\n<li>Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:</li>\r\n\t<ul style=\"font-size:16px\">\r\n    \t<li>Key roles and responsibilities</li>\r\n\t\t<li>Key challenges</li>\r\n\t\t<li>How computing supports their work</li>\r\n\t\t<li>How your chosen innovation helps their job</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n<br/>\r\n<li>Summarize key insights in your activity guide.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n",
    "aichat_settings": {
      "initialCustomizations": {
